          <p>We implement strong security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or misuse.</p>
          
          <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party services for analytics and advertising purposes, ensuring compliance with privacy regulations.</p>
          
          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data. Contact us for any requests regarding your information.</p>
